b \gt 2
\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\frac{n!}{b(b+1)...(b+n-1)}=\frac{1}{b-2}
\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\frac{n!(b-2)}{(b-2)b(b+1)...(b+n-1)}=\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\frac{n!(b+n-1-2+1-n)}{(b-2)b(b+1)...(b+n-1)}=\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\frac{n!(b+n-1)-(1+n)}{(b-2)b(b+1)...(b+n-1)}=\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\frac{n!(b+n-1)}{(b-2)b(b+1)...(b+n-1)}-\frac{n!(1+n)}{(b-2)b(b+1)...(b+n-1)}=\frac{1}{b-2}\left(\frac{b-2}{b}+\sum_{n=2}^{\infty}\frac{n!}{b(b+1)...(b+n-2)}-\frac{(n+1)!}{b(b+1)....(b+n-1)}\right)
S_n=\frac{1}{b-2}\left[\frac{b-2}{b}+\left(\frac{2}{b}-\frac{3!}{b(b+1)}\right)+\left(\frac{3!}{b(b+1)}-\frac{4!}{b(b+1)(b+2)}\right)+...+\left(\frac{n!}{b(b+1)..(b+n-2)}-\frac{(n+1)!}{b(b+1)...(b+n-1)}\right)\right]=\frac{1}{b-2}\left[1-\frac{(n+1)!}{b(b+1)..(b+n-1)}\right]
\lim\limits_{n\to \infty}\frac{(n+1)!}{b(b+1)..(b+n-1)}=0
\lim_{n\to\infty}\frac{(n+1)!}{b(b+1)\cdot...\cdot(b+n-1)}=\lim_{n\to\infty}\frac{n!n^{b}}{b(b+1)\cdot...\cdot(b+n-1)(b+n)}\cdot\frac{(n+1)(b+n)}{n^{b}}
=\lim_{n\to\infty}\frac{n!n^{b}}{b(b+1)\cdot...\cdot(b+n)}\cdot\frac{(1+\frac{1}{n})(1+\frac{b}{n})}{n^{b-2}}=\Gamma(b)\lim_{n\to\infty}\frac{(1+\frac{1}{n})(1+\frac{b}{n})}{n^{b-2}}=0
b>2
\lim_{n\to\infty}\frac{(1+\frac{1}{n})(1+\frac{b}{n})}{n^{b-2}}
